Titolo: Mission Critical (video game)

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Mission Critical is an adventure game released in 1995 by Legend Entertainment. Though its main advertising point was the presence of Star Trek: The Next Generation actor Michael Dorn, he played a very small role in the game, the main author being Legend CEO Mike Verdu. The game also featured a leading role by American actress Patricia Charbonneau, best known for her role in the film Desert Hearts.
The player takes on the role of the sole survivor of the USS Lexington and USS Jericho, a pair of starships sent by the Alliance of Free States that are ambushed on a secret scientific mission to Deneb Kaitos.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
